room_title: Escape room "The Lost Temple" by Escape FLA in Tampa
room_description:
Several decades ago Dr. Oklahoma Smith went on a solo expedition to try and recover the Ixcacao Idol from the Temple of Xocolatl. Unfortunately Dr. Smith never returned. Will your team have the skills necessary to pass the tests devised by the ancient Gods? 

Fame and fortune await if you succeed. If you do not...
